<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxyc577d6fa0c114bb68493b38451e386b9-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent5b312687d1c4437da1b7d1595dc30410">
</div>
<p>There are large car parks for patients and visitors, for which charges apply. To view charges, please vlew our website. Some visitors are exempt from payment: eg: parents staying overnight with very sick children; patients undergoing treatment such as radiotherapy; parents feeding babies on the Neo Natal Unit. <a href="http://www.gloshospitals.nhs.uk/content/transport.html">Click Here</a></p>
